== spies.js

This is a javascript spy framework that was extracted from Corey Haines and Sarah Gray's work on The Stickies Project (http://thestickiesproject.heroku.com). 


== Using spies.js

1. Put spies.js in an accessible place in your application.
2. Include it in your specs
3. Use it according to the examples (located in spies_spec.js)


